            <sentence>
                <offset>1755</offset>
                <text>With all of these clinical, physical examination,&#13;
laboratory, and radiological findings, the patient&#13;
was diagnosed with Caffey disease.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1893</offset>
                <text>In genetic&#13;
investigation, heterozygous missense mutation&#13;
(c.3040C&gt;T) in COL1A1 gene was detected&#13;
in our patient with sequence analyzes method&#13;
(Fig. 2).</text>
